							},
							"Translation": {
								"Text": ""
							},
							"Key": "NoCompanion"
						},
						{
							"Source": {
								"Text": "No lore available."
							},
							"Translation": {
								"Text": "沒有神話可用。"
							},
							"Key": "FallbackLore"
						},
						{
							"Source": {
								"Text": "Once a wanderer, now sworn to protect the fallen."
							},
							"Translation": {
								"Text": "曾經是流浪者 現在發誓保護掉下去的人"
							},
							"Key": "Companion_03"
						},
						{
							"Source": {
								"Text": "The last of her kind, fighting to survive."
							},
